 Beese Fulmer believes it makes sense to invest sensibly in the present, so there is something to invest in the future.


The family that invests together does best together. Your Beese Fulmer family wealth advisors started the firm over 34 years ago, concentrating solely on only a few of the area's truly wealthy families. That's when we decided that rational investment planning and holistic control made the most sense.
A family is an investment unit
Its an investment unit with unique needs. While privacy is of the utmost importance to us, we urge family members to work together to overcome the more complicated wealth dilemmas.
Closely-held stock can concentrate a family’s wealth around one company.
Family foundations can be a tax-efficient vehicle.
End-of-life care should be addressed before it’s too late.
Making annual gifts to children and grand children.
Working with your attorney and accountant to design trusts and other efficient methods to pass wealth to future generations.
Building overall family wealth leads to greater flexibility and security for future generations. Let Beese Fulmer help you and your family build on the wealth you worked so hard to acquire.
 
