Company Overview of Beese, Fulmer Investment Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Beese, Fulmer Investment Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. It manages separate client focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It primarily invests in growth stocks of companies to make its equity investments. The firm also invests in fixed income securities including, corporate bonds, municipal bonds, and individual bonds. It limits the maturities to ten years or less on all fixed income securities. The firm employs a f...
Beese, Fulmer Investment Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to individuals, high net worth individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. It manages separate client focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It primarily invests in growth stocks of companies to make its equity investments. The firm also invests in fixed income securities including, corporate bonds, municipal bonds, and individual bonds. It limits the maturities to ten years or less on all fixed income securities. The firm employs a fundamental analysis to create its portfolios. Beese, Fulmer Investment Management, Inc. was founded in 1980 and is based in Canton, Ohio.
Detailed Description


