			Some people have told us that we're a little slow to jump on the newest thing. We take that as a compliment… and an endorsement. Beese Fulmer doesn't jump. We are the wealth management advisors who think first and act later. This has made our clients happier and their investments healthier. Beese Fulmer Private Wealth Management LIVES by The Rules of the Rational:Emotions are the enemy of the successful investorShort-term investing leads to long-term disappointmentThere is NO alternative to high qualityBuy superior securities at the right price – A great company is not always a great stockEliminate the middle man – Trust the expertsMaximize wealth building – Minimize taxes, expenses, and feesViewing all assets on one statement is an assetBeing diversified is just as important as avoiding too much diversificationPortfolio management should complement your tax and estate-planning strategiesTrusting your investment manager is half the battle Make sure you see the whole picture... 







